txt.en: The Battle of Uzdarulzahar has begun!\n\nYou should defeat drakes in Uzdarulzahar.
The Frost-horde has come to assist the hobgoblins in the Battle of Uzdarulzahar.
You have defeated many drakes of the Frost-horde in Uzdarulzahar, turning the tide of battle in favour of the Gabil'akkâ!
The drakes of the Frost-horde have arrived to assist the hobgoblins in the Battle of Uzdarulzahar. You should defeat them to ensure victory for the Gabil'akkâ!
